column7: Oh oh oh oh really Zag another offering, for me, why I just don't know what to say, except for: Cheers! And, here, a gift from me!
You got good taste, I ever tell you, man? And I got good taste too, so I'll be certain to enjoy your little offering, and you go enjoy this!
You want to tangle with us?!
Oh hey man, what is new?
Hey you hanging in there yeah?
You still in one piece, man?
Sounds good to me there Zag.
Hey now that is something, yeah!
I can't say no to that!
Oh yeah I dig it man!
Have I got just the thing for you!
Eh not exactly what I had in mind.
What can I say, man, it's a shame all right.
Now don't be like that man.
Knew you could do it man!
Hahaha, don't you know it, man!
Oh we are going to have a feast tonight!
Ooh you're in a real heap of trouble, Zag!
Yeaaah, man, you know what it's all about!
Hah, cheers to you, then, man!
That definitely was a good decision, man!
Didn't have to be like this, man! We were having such a good time!
Hate to sour the occasion like this, Zag. What was I supposed to do?
Eugh, I feel bad all of a sudden, man, I mean, what happened, there?
